sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor User
  participant FE as Frontend
  participant API as Django API
  participant VS as Qdrant Vector Store
  participant LLM as LLM Provider
  participant DB as PostgreSQL

  User->>FE: Submit question
  FE->>API: POST /api/chat/messages
  API->>VS: similarity_search(query)
  VS-->>API: top-k chunks
  API->>LLM: generate(context + question)
  LLM-->>API: answer + confidence
  API->>DB: save message + metrics
  DB-->>API: saved
  API-->>FE: response + sources
  FE-->>User: Render answer
